# Research assistant (/api/research).
# Works with NO key: it answers from the model's own SHAP output for free.
# Add a free Google AI Studio key to upgrade it to a live LLM (Gemini free tier).
# Server-side only — never exposed to the browser. Copy to .env.local for local dev,
# or set it as an env var in your host (e.g. Vercel). Get a key: aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the Gemini model (defaults to gemini-2.0-flash).
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash

# Optional: point the frontend at the FastAPI backend instead of the built-in /api routes.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
